        "body": [
            {
                "type": "section", 
                "id": "s0", 
                "title": "Main text", 
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "Qu\u00e9net D, Dalal Y. 2014. A long non-coding RNA is required for targeting centromeric protein A to the human centromere. <i>eLife</i> <b>3</b>:e03254. doi: <a href=\"http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/eLife.03254\">10.7554/eLife.03254</a>. Published 12 August 2014"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "An error has been brought to our attention whereby there is duplication of two panels, within Figure 1A (top left panel) and a control panel inside Figure 3C (top left panel). Both images, which were inadvertently duplicated during figure preparation, display co-immuno-fluorescence of RNAPII<sup>S2P</sup> and CENP-B performed on chromatin fibers extracted from eG1-synchronized HeLa cells."
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "In this correction, we replace the top left panel in Figure 3C with a different chromatin fiber acquired under exactly the same conditions. The conclusions are unaffected and we apologize for the original mistake."
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The corrected Figure 3 is shown here:"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "image", 
                        "id": "fig1", 
                        "alt": "", 
                        "uri": "https://publishing-cdn.elifesciences.org/07239/elife-07239-fig1-v1.tif", 
                        "filename": "elife-07239-fig1-v1.tif"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The originally published Figure 3 is also shown for reference:"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "image", 
                        "id": "fig2", 
                        "alt": "", 
                        "uri": "https://publishing-cdn.elifesciences.org/07239/elife-07239-fig2-v1.tif", 
                        "filename": "elife-07239-fig2-v1.tif"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The article has been corrected accordingly."
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
